# BeSmart core

- Expo 56: use versioned docs at https://docs.expo.dev/versions/v56.0.0/
- Import alias: `@/` → `src/`
- Routes live in `src/app/` (not root `app/`)
- User state: `useApp()` from `@/context/app-context`, backed by `userStore`
- Content types in `src/types/learning.ts` and `src/types/book.ts`
- Data public API: `src/data/index.ts`
- See AGENTS.md for full map before exploring the repo
- Update AGENTS.md only on architecture changes — not per feature (see "Maintaining this map")
